tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE MedicalSuppliesInventory (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    item_name VARCHAR(255),
    quantity INT,
    expiration_date DATE,
    location VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE inventory (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    item_id UUID,
    item_type VARCHAR(50),
    quantity INT,
    location VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE inventory (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  item_id INT,
  item_type VARCHAR,
  quantity INT,
  location VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE purchase_orders (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  supplier_id UUID,
  item_id UUID,
  quantity INT,
  order_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE inventory_history (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  item_id UUID,
  action STRING,
  quantity_change INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
